sequenceDiagram
    participant Ops as Ops admin or service client
    participant API as TransferReversalController
    participant Policy as ReversalValidationPolicy
    participant Ledger as LedgerPostingUseCase
    participant Audit as AuditEventWriter
    participant Outbox as OutboxWriterService
    participant DB as Oracle

    Ops->>API: POST /api/v1/transfers/{id}/reverse
    API->>Policy: validate original transfer can be reversed
    Policy->>DB: read original transfer and ledger transaction
    API->>Ledger: post opposite journal lines
    Ledger->>DB: insert reversal ledger transaction and postings
    API->>DB: insert reversal request and mark original transfer reversed
    API->>Audit: write reversal audit event
    Audit->>DB: insert audit event
    API->>Outbox: write reversal and balance events
    Outbox->>DB: insert pending outbox events
    API-->>Ops: 201 reversal response
